stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initializing: main.py starts
    
    Initializing --> Running: start() called
    
    Running --> Trading: enable_trading event
    Running --> Paused: disable_trading event
    
    Trading --> Paused: disable_trading event
    Paused --> Trading: enable_trading event
    
    Trading --> Emergency: emergency_stop event
    Paused --> Emergency: emergency_stop event
    Running --> Emergency: emergency_stop event
    
    Emergency --> Paused: Recovery complete
    
    Trading --> Stopped: stop() called
    Paused --> Stopped: stop() called
    Emergency --> Stopped: stop() called
    Running --> Stopped: stop() called
    
    Stopped --> [*]
    
    Running: System Online<br/>is_running = True<br/>is_trading_enabled = False
    Trading: Active Trading<br/>is_running = True<br/>is_trading_enabled = True<br/>✅ Workflows Execute
    Paused: Standby Mode<br/>is_running = True<br/>is_trading_enabled = False<br/>⏸️ No Workflows
    Emergency: Emergency Mode<br/>is_running = True<br/>is_trading_enabled = False<br/>🚨 Closing Positions
    Stopped: System Shutdown<br/>is_running = False

